quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  11,41,"Inna: \"rekbet degs, s yisem n Öebbi, acali s akked trusi s. Mass iw, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  11,42,"Icula yissen, di lemwao anect idurar. Issawel Nuê i mmi s, i illan weêdes: \"a mmi ali d yidne$, ur teppiliv ar ijehliyen"
  11,43,"Inna: \"ûûôan iw d adrar, ad iyi isellek seg waman\". Inna: \"assa, ulac leslak si lameô n Öebbi, siwa i win i$ef Iêun\". Âaddant lemwao garasen. Iûebê ed seg wid ipwa$emqen"
  11,44,"Nnan: \"a tamurt, seblaâ aman im, a yigenni eûûfu\". Aman zzren. Iûaô lameô: irs $ef Loudi. Iffe$ uberraê: akin agdud imednas"
  11,45,"Inuj Nuê ar Mass is, inna: \"a Mass iw! Ni$ mmi n twacult iw. Ih, lemâahda K d tidep, Keçç Tifev akw imêaddan"
  11,46,"Inna: \"a Nuê! Neppa, s tidep, ur illi n wacult ik. Ih, neppa ur ixdim ayen ilhan. Ihi, ur iyI d steqsay $ef wayen ur tessinev. Nek a k Ssakwaye$, ur teppiliv seg wid ur nessin"
  11,47,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Ili di lâawen iw, iwakken ur K id steqsaye$ $ef wayen ur ssine$. Ma ur iyi Tsemmêev, ur Têunev felli, ad ili$ seg imexsuôen"
  11,48,"Nnan d: \"a Nuê! Ers ed s tifrat s$uône£, akked lbaôaka, fellak akw $ef leoyus i illan yidek. Kra n legyus, a ten N$it. Sinna, fellasen s$uône£, aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  11,49,"Tagi si teqûivin n tbavnit, Nweêêa yak tent. Ur tent tessinev, keçç, ne$ agdud ik, uqbel wagi. Ihi, eûbeô, taggara, war ccekk, i wid ipêezziben"
  11,50,"I Âad, gmat sen Hud, inna: \"a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Kunwi tesnulfuyem d kan"
  11,51,"A yagdud iw! Ur awen ssuture$ taqdiât $ef waya. Taqdiât iw ar Win kan, iyi d Ixelqen. Day ur tefhimem ara"
  11,52,"A yagdud iw! Ssutret ssmaê i Mass nnwen, sinna, steôoâet aS. Ad awen d Isse$li ageffur d ihedman, ad awen irnu tazmert i tezmert nnwen. Ur ppu$alet d ibe$wviyen"
  11,53,"Nnan as: \"a Hud! Ur a$ d tusid s ubeggen, ur neppaoa, nekwni, iôebbiten nne$, ilmend n wawal ik, ur numin yisek"
  11,54,"Neqqaô kan, d kra iôebbiten nne$, i k i$eôqen\". Inna: \"nek, Anagi w d Öebbi, u cehhdet ar ur ppka$ ara deg wayen tepcarakem"
  11,55,"war Neppa. Ihi, andit iyi akken ma tellam, sinna ur iyi sganayet"
  11,56,"Nek, ppekle$ af Öebbi, Mass iw u Mass nnwen. Ur illi umexluq ur Iîîif seg ixef is. Ih, Mass iw deg ubrid uwqim"
  11,57,"Ma wexxôen, ni$ ssawve$ awen d ayen i$ef id ppuceggâa$ $uôwen. A d Inûef, Mass iw, agdud war kunwi. Ur T teîîuôum s wacemma. Mass iw, s tidep, d Amêareb n yal cci"
  11,58,"Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nsellek Hud akked wid iumnen yides, s uêunu s$uône£. Nsellek iten seg uâaqeb uwâiô"
  11,59,"Akka Âad. Nekôen issekniyen n Mass nnsen, âuûan imazanen iS. Ddan d lameô n yal aqehhaô iggernennen"
  11,60,"A ten ivfeô xezzu di ddunit agi, u deg wass n tnekra. Day, war ccekk, ur jhilen ara Âad, ar Mass nnsen? Day maççi: \"akin Âad, agdud n Hud"